    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! You\u2019ve seriously got to see this beauty in person. It\u2019s in absolutely incredible shape\u2014honestly, it feels like it just rolled off the showroom floor! I\u2019ve babied this car since day one, and it\u2019s been kept spotless inside and out. It drives like a total dream and looks even better. If you\u2019re looking for that perfect, like-new ride without the brand-new price tag, this is definitely the one for you. Drop me a message and come take a look! \u2728",
      "price": 46500.0,
