      "description": "Presented in superlative condition, this vehicle represents the pinnacle of its class. Every detail, from the flawless exterior finish to the pristine interior, has been maintained to an exacting standard. Mechanically, the vehicle performs with the precision of a showroom model, offering an uncompromising driving experience for the discerning buyer. This is a rare opportunity to acquire a specimen of such distinguished quality and preserved integrity.",
      "price": 48500.0,
