    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey friends! \ud83d\ude97 I'm parting with my absolute pride and joy. This beauty is in truly pristine, mint condition\u2014honestly, it still has that 'new car' feel! I\u2019ve babied it since day one, kept it garage-parked, and it runs like a dream. If you\u2019re looking for a ride that\u2019s basically flawless and ready for a new home, this is the one. Come take a look, you\u2019re going to love it!",
      "price": 44900.0,
