      "description": "This E46 M3 is a definitive collector-grade example featuring the high-revving S54B32 power plant. The engine exhibits perfect compression across all six cylinders, with the dual-VANOS system and rod bearings proactively serviced to ensure peak mechanical integrity. The Getrag 6-speed manual transmission shifts with bolt-action precision, delivering power through a factory variable M differential lock. Crucially, the rear subframe has been reinforced, preserving the chassis's torsional rigidity. Finished in immaculate original paint with a flawless interior, this vehicle remains in showroom condition, free of the typical wear on seat bolsters or suspension bushings. A true turn-key masterpiece for the purist.",
